-- Bridges Ventures Seeks to Sell U.K. Gym Chain, Independent Says
-- B y   M i c h e l l e   W i e s e   B o c k m a n n
-- 2012-06-03T15:26:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-03/bridges-ventures-seeks-to-sell-u-k-gym-chain-independent-says.html
Bridges Ventures Ltd., a U.K. private
equity fund, is preparing to sell fitness centre chain  The Gym
Group  for more than 100 million pounds ($154 million), the
Independent on Sunday reported, without saying where it got the
information.  Corporate adviser  McQueen Ltd  is in the very early stages
of reviewing the business and looking for a buyer for the chain
of 23 gyms, with a deal not expected until 2013, according to
the newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Michelle Wiese Bockmann in London at 
